==Maltese==
===Etymology===
From {{der|mt|ar|شَلُوق}}, {{m|ar|شَلُوك|t=southeastern wind}}, probably acquired through Italo-{{der|mt|roa}}, see {{cog|it|scirocco}}. A doublet may be at hand in {{m|mt|xellug|t=left}}, which see.
